**Initiative:** Converting Feature-Complete UI to Production-Ready  
**Date:** February 10, 2026  
**Role:** Principal Frontend Engineer  
**Tech Stack:** React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + Vite + Framer Motion

